And we don't have everything always figured out, but we're trying.

00:59:33.581 --> 00:59:40.458
God bless you all. We love you. Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:59:40.459 --> 00:59:50.680
Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless you all and we'll see you again soon. Bye bye.

